to onclick. we then set onclick to a JS function "clearInterval" this predifined function stops the numbers from climbing. inside of the 
clear interval parameter are will be placed a variable from our JS page "myCounter" this is the variable that actually initiates the 
interval so it must be place within clearInterval if the numbers are to stop climbing.-->
        <p id="counter">0</p>
        <p><button onclick="clearInterval(myCounter)">Stop Counting</button></p>
